			Profile
			
			Dr.ZouisanassociateprofessorinInstituteofMateriaMedica,CollegeofPharmaceuticalSciencesatZhejiangUniversity,China.
&nbsp;
Dr.Zoustartedundergraduatetrainingfrom1998andreceivedhisbachelordegreeofscienceinCollegeofPharmaceuticalSciencesZhejiangUniversity.In2007,DrZoureceivedhisPh.DdegreeinmedicinalchemistryfromZhejiangUniversity,wherehecarriedoutstructureoptimizationandbioactivityevaluationofbioactivenaturalproductsderivatives.Then,hecompletedpostdoctoralworkattheUniversityofJohannesGutenbergUniversityMainz(MainzUniversity)Germany,wherehestudiedstructurebiologyandenzymaticchemistryofstrictosidinesynthase,thekeyenzymeofalkaloidbiosynthesis.
&nbsp;
Dr.ZouwasselectedasQianjiangTalentedScholarofZhejiangProvinceandoneofthefirstDistinguishedQiushiYoungScientistsofZhejiangUniversityforhisdistinguishedscientificresearch.
&nbsp;
