			Researchwork
			
			ThemainfocusofourlabistoChemicalbiologystudyonbiosyntheticapproachtobiologicalactivenaturalmetabolitesandtheirpotentialtherapeuticvalue.Weareespeciallyinterestedinthebiosyntheticenzymeandgeneclustersinvolvedinbioactivenaturalproductsbiosynthesissuchasalkaloids.Invitroutilizationoftheselinkedenzymes,suchasenzymaticchemistry,arecarriedouttomakebioactivesmallmoleculelibrarieswithdiversificationfordrugdiscovery.
			
				
